OL,5, Pope Francis has no intention of       
OL,6, retiring and plans to remain in post   
OL,7, for life, according to his new         
OL,8, autobiography.                         
OL,10,FIn "Life: My Story Through History",   
OL,11,FPope Francis, who is 87, says there is 
OL,12,F"no risk" of him resigning despite     
OL,13,Fspeculation he might step down         
OL,14,Ffollowing a spate of health issues.    
OL,16,F"I believe the pope's ministry is ad   
OL,17,Fvitam, for life," Francis says.        
OL,19,F"I therefore see no justification for  
OL,20,Fgiving it up."                         
